	"title": "Initial Release (0.1.0)",
	"body": "## What's Changed\r\n* Rename project to Discussion Kit and update configurations by @NotReeceHarris in https://github.com/NotReeceHarris/discussion-kit/pull/5\r\n* Refactor authentication and improve discussion loading logic by @NotReeceHarris in https://github.com/NotReeceHarris/discussion-kit/pull/7\r\n* Implement moderation features and discussion management capabilities by @NotReeceHarris in https://github.com/NotReeceHarris/discussion-kit/pull/9\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @NotReeceHarris made their first contribution in https://github.com/NotReeceHarris/discussion-kit/pull/5\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/NotReeceHarris/discussion-kit/commits/v0.1.0\n\n<hr /><em>This discussion was created from the release <a href='https://github.com/NotReeceHarris/discussion-kit/releases/tag/v0.1.0'>Initial Release (0.1.0)</a>.</em>",
